XHEADER.Title: Refresh Alfresco Schema in Saks DR from Saks Prod

DOCU_Docu.DOC: # Script for refreshing ALFRESCO42 schema in Saks DR from Saks Prod # # !!!!!! Alfresco Application has to be stopped in Saks DR before exeucting this script, else this will FAIL !!!!! # #

XHEADER.Title: hd4palf01lx alfresco instance will be brought down

SCRIPT.MSCRI:
#!/bin/bash ################################################################################# # The script acts as a wrapper script to stop alfresco instance # for Saks DR Prod Environments. # Developed By: Chinmay Bhatawdekar #################################################################################
ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "/home/alfresco/blue/apache-tomcat-7.0.42/alfresco.sh stop" ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "kill -9 `ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com 'cat /home/alfresco/blue/apache-tomcat-7.0.42/alfresco.pid'`"

XHEADER.Title: hd4palf01lx alfresco instance will be brought UP

SCRIPT.MSCRI:
#!/bin/bash ################################################################################# # The script acts as a wrapper script to start alfresco instance. # for Saks DR Production Environments. # Developed By: Chinmay Bhatawdekar #################################################################################
FILEPATH="/home/alfresco/blue/apache-tomcat-7.0.42/alfresco.pid" ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "test -e $FILEPATH" if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then PIDNO=`ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "cat $FILEPATH"` ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "ps -ef | grep $PIDNO | grep -v grep" if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then echo "Server Failed to shutdown, Forcing server shutdown" ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "kill -9 $PIDNO" fi ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "rm $FILEPATH" fi sleep 60 ssh alfresco@hd4palf01lx.digital.hbc.com "/home/alfresco/blue/apache-tomcat-7.0.42/alfresco.sh start"
